    <note>Zhao(1) Heng [9003] Taizong's [9002] third son, Renzong's [9004] father. Zhang(1) Zhaoyun's [7149] brother-in-law. His first empress was Pan(1) Mei's [1389] daughter (who died in 989 at the age of 22), and his third empress was the younger sister of Ma(2) Jiliang's [1342] father-in-law, Liu(2) Mei [3598]. Li(2) Ying(3) [7281] was his maternal grandfather. He was the maternal grandfather of Qian(1) Weiyan's [8006] son, Hui [3034]. CBD, 3, 2144 (empress Guo, who died in 1007 at age 32); CBD, 5, 3643 (empress Pan). CBD, 1, 774.</note>
